# GAN 356i Experiments

The newest release (v3.2.0 JUL 2019 US Nationals) seems to obfuscate the data.

The older (v3.1.0) one has pretty transparent data. The newer appears to be the same data but obfuscated in some one.

# Count + Twists (`fff3`)

Looking at `fff3` while twisting R repeatedly. On the old cube, this reports a count (first byte) followed by a history of 18 twists (3 for R). So this should represent a count byte followed by a bunch of 3s.
